GRANT v. WARDEN OF MARYLAND HOUSE OF CORRECTION [App. No. 83,

September Term, 1965.]

Decided January 6, 1966. Before Prescott, C. J., and Hammond, HornEy, Marbury,. Oppenheimer and McWilliams, JJ. *740PER Curiam.

Eor the reasons set forth in the opinion of Judge Macgill in the lower court, the application for leave to appeal is denied.

Application denied.
